    "body": "We have done a lot of bikeshedding on this already. Any further changes\nwill need to be supported by data. If there is evidence that the proposed\nchange will directly improve an actual use case, please present it.\n\nThanks\n-Abhishek\nOn Jul 31, 2015 9:02 AM, \"Carl Mastrangelo\" notifications@github.com\nwrote:\n\n> INITIAL_BACKOFF =(5 + 3 \\* SQRT(5))/10\n> \n> ## MULTIPLIER = (SQRT(5)+1)/2\n> \n> You can view, comment on, or merge this pull request online at:\n> \n>   https://github.com/grpc/grpc/pull/2738\n> Commit Summary\n> - Make backoff policy based on closed form fibonacci growth\n> \n> File Changes\n> - _M_ doc/connection-backoff.md\n>   https://github.com/grpc/grpc/pull/2738/files#diff-0 (7)\n> \n> Patch Links:\n> - https://github.com/grpc/grpc/pull/2738.patch\n> - https://github.com/grpc/grpc/pull/2738.diff\n> \n> â€”\n> Reply to this email directly or view it on GitHub\n> https://github.com/grpc/grpc/pull/2738.\n"
